":guilabel:`Revenues`, :guilabel:`Quotations`, :guilabel:`Opportunities` і "
":guilabel:`Clicks`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing.rst:779
msgid ""
"There are also buttons to :guilabel:`Send Mailing`, :guilabel:`Send "
"SMS`, :guilabel:`Add Post`, and :guilabel:`Add Push` (push notification)."
msgstr ""
"Також є кнопки для :guilabel:`Send Mailing`, :guilabel:`Send SMS`, "
